adding: 15px 0;color: #fff;\">\n    <div class=\"footer-seo\">\n        <h2>NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones: Unleash Wireless Freedom with Unmatched Comfort<\/h2>\n        \n        <h3>Innovative Open-Ear Technology<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            Crafted for those who crave both situational awareness and exceptional audio fidelity, the NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones redefine how you experience sound. Using innovative <strong>open-ear technology<\/strong>, these headphones rest gently above your ears, allowing ambient sounds like a passing car or a friendly greeting to filter through naturally while enveloping you in crisp, immersive audio. Whether you're navigating a bustling city street or enjoying a quiet evening at home, you’ll stay connected to your surroundings without sacrificing sound quality.\n        <\/p>\n        \n        <h3>Lightweight Design and Long-Lasting Battery<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            With a <strong>featherlight and ergonomic design<\/strong>, weighing just 28 grams, NG EarSafe headphones contour seamlessly to your ears, offering a barely-there feel that’s perfect for extended wear. Picture yourself powering through a marathon work session, embarking on a scenic commute, or pushing your limits at the gym. These headphones deliver all-day comfort without the pressure of traditional earbuds. Plus, their robust <strong>IPX5 water-resistant rating<\/strong> ensures they can withstand sweat or a sudden drizzle, making them a reliable companion for any adventure. With an impressive <strong>8-hour battery life<\/strong>, extendable to 24 hours with the sleek charging case, you’ll enjoy uninterrupted music, podcasts, or calls from dawn to dusk without scrambling for a charger.\n        <\/p>\n        \n        <h3>Advanced Connectivity and Clear Communication<\/h3>\n        <p>\n            Fueled by cutting-edge <strong>Bluetooth 5.0 technology<\/strong>, the NG EarSafe headphones provide a rock-solid wireless connection up to 33 feet, banishing frustrating dropouts and audio lag even in crowded environments. The integrated <strong>high-sensitivity microphone<\/strong>, enhanced with noise-canceling features, captures your voice with crystal-clear precision, transforming chaotic commutes into effortless hands-free conversations. Available in stylish shades like Midnight Black and Arctic White, these headphones don’t just perform. They make a statement. Whether you’re syncing to your favorite playlist, catching up with a friend, or unwinding with an audiobook, the NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones fuse safety, sophistication, and stellar sound into one game-changing package. Elevate your listening journey today!\n        <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n    .footer-seo {color:#ddd;padding:30px;text-align:left;border-radius:8px}\n    .footer-seo h2 {color:#fff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo h3 {color:#fff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo p {font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n<\/style>","layout":"t4s-container-fluid","cl_bg":"#252525","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,0px,","pd":"","mg_tb":"","pd_tb":"","mg_mb":",,0px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}}},"order":["breadcrumb","main","slideshow_H9HCWW","sidebar","fcc64674-be8f-4eb2-8f04-0bacf8de5771","21cc52cf-8bcf-42ba-8f07-80d94e7a589e","df43a99b-eda3-4c32-837f-b6640989c695","601092f3-f61a-4147-b4f4-33b069d7f348","a0e3c96b-09ad-4fe8-90fe-4e91deedd752","617310e4-15e9-4543-82e0-1f050ae4ab1e","4bce7335-2a2b-4e8a-b006-05c8651811f8","2f8947bb-a208-4ff1-92dd-ca00313dd658","27a62662-0e46-4637-a877-1f6c3f2decbb","87df8b17-dc27-449b-ba9a-eb084958bb91","04fbdf0e-5386-4930-b05f-10d6e52f33bf","ec8915fe-2aff-44fc-b59d-72b690f5e071","14f54523-b5e7-4690-b573-83b33831d4e9","77561158-d4b4-412b-a5a2-42695c15bc02","accordion_4NGXHR","1737282429ed5d4301","83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0","product-recommendations","recently-viewed-products","image_text_6wLq8M"